summary:
Communicative, hands on, with a wide range of skills and talents. Experienced in many different work environments, and specialised in language and linguistics. I love and have practised both face to face communication, customer service and problem solving as well as teaching English as second language and meticulous technical work with words.
Eye for detail, patience, effectiveness and productivity in one. Dedication, consistency and eagerness to learn and offer; I appreciate creativity, honesty, goals and achievements, and versatile, informal, dynamic and challenging business environments.
